> Nutty Ford Farm Coastal Cheddar, Hawes Wensleydale & Cranberry, creamy French
> Camembert, and a ripe Fourme D'ambert make up the winning selection for our
> delicious cheese board. Served with crackers and chutney, this is a wonderful
> addition to our Christmas Box, perfect for sharing.